MEDIA personality Boity Thulo and actor boyfriend Anton Jeftha have opened up about their relationship. The private couple played a couple’s quiz on Instagram, sharing about how and when they met and their first date. Each had 12 questions to ask each other. One of the first things Boity asked Anton was where they met. He said: “The date was 23 January this year. You know how I know? It’s cause it was my mum’s birthday.” ALSO READ : THANDISWA SHARES MEMORY OF TATA AND KING OF POP! They spilled the details about their first date, where they went to and what they ate. Boity also asked Anton questions like what she’s most afraid of, what she wanted to be when she was young and other questions, which he mostly answered correctly. When it was his turn, he asked where he was born, where he went to university and what he studied and Boity got all the answers right. The couple started off by hiding their relationship and claimed to be friends for a while. Now they no longer hide that they’re together. Watch them below. A post shared by Anton David Jeftha (@antonjeftha) 